9.Ng6 Rh7 10.e5 { with a huge advantage } ) 9.Qf3+ $1 Kxe5 10.Qf7 $1
{ [%csl Re5] } Ngf6 11.Rd1
{ and the king is unable to escape. After the text move White also has a spectacular tactical trick. }
) 6.dxe5 dxe5 { # } ( 6...Nxe5 $2 7.Nxe5 dxe5 8.Qh5
{ loses a pawn as we've seen before. } ) 7.Ng5 $1 Bxg5 ( { In case of }
7...Nh6 { White may strike another blow - } 8.Ne6 $1 fxe6 9.Bxh6 Nb6 $1 ( 
